The paper discusses Multi-Task Learning (MTL) algorithms and their applications in machine learning. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.LG (Machine Learning), as MTL is a learning paradigm in machine learning. The paper also discusses MTL in the context of computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR), which are all related to machine learning. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of MTL with reinforcement learning (cs.AI) and graphical models (cs.SI), which are also relevant sub-categories.
